public class IString
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.CharSequence, java.io.Serializable, HasIntegerIdentity, HasWord, java.lang.Comparable<IString>

Represents a String with a corresponding integer ID. Keeps a static index of all the Strings, indexed by ID.
